Cell["\<\
to precisely the same result.

To obtain all possible effective resistance values one would\[LongDash]if \
using the variational method\[LongDash]have to repeatedly adjust the \
constraint equations and re-calculate. But the Klein-Randi\[CAcute] method \
supplies them all at once:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5289270727260237`*^9, 3.528927079990192*^9}, {
  3.5289323202663383`*^9, 3.5289323204733*^9}, {3.528932359781351*^9, 
  3.528932543766961*^9}}],

